================================================================================
Project authorship
================================================================================

BadBlood-Revival was created and is maintained by MrPie (Filip Otto).
Original work in this repository includes:

  - Server emulator (FastAPI Python backend re-implementing Techland's
    proprietary PLS protocol — auth, profile, inventory, shop, leaderboards,
    friends, matchmaking relay)
  - Win32/Direct3D 11 launcher with ImGui UI
  - Client patcher (Python, applies byte-level patches to a vanilla install)
  - DLL hooks for runtime texture replacement and DNS redirection
  - Empty replacement DLLs (stubs) for EasyAntiCheat and BattlEye
  - Reverse engineering of the PLS auth flow, the engine HTTP transport
    gate field at [+0x80], the EAC launcher-check bypass at 0x6F73DE,
    the CURLOPT_SSL_VERIFY* bypass instructions, the rpacz filename
    whitelist, the RP6L rpack file format, and the RCreateTexture2D
    interception point in rd3d11

